{"tid":1333332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】因管理不善而在全球最佳航空排名榜節節下跌的國泰航空，已完成收購香港快運航空","createTime":"2019-07-19T15:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T18:48:58.000Z","uid":66271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5029613f8dcd1e12fb9e07f16c87d84233f911b4","tid":1333332,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.uc.assets.prezly.com/c0efd975-5b18-4f70-85b4-59033656cb06/-/resize/1108x/-/quality/best/-/format/auto/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uc.assets.prezly.com%2Fc0efd975-5b18-4f70-85b4-59033656cb06%2F-%2Fresize%2F1108x%2F-%2Fquality%2Fbest%2F-%2Fformat%2Fauto%2F&h=75ba506c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年7月19日星期五 &mdash; 國泰航空宣佈，已完成收購香港快運航空(香港快運)。香港快運現為國泰航空的全資附屬公司。<br />\n國泰航空行政總裁及香港快運主席何杲表示：「我們非常高興香港快運成為國泰集團一份子。我們深信這宗收購有利旅客；有利香港快運；有利國泰航空，有利進一步鞏固香港國際機場的樞紐地位。<br />\n<br />\n「我們會與香港快運團隊緊密合作，確保過渡安排及工作暢順，繼續發展其航空業務，為乘客提供更稱心的服務。」<br />\n<br />\n香港快運行政總裁林紹波會帶領公司團隊發展業務。林紹波已在國泰航空集團和港機工程公司工作二十多年，之前為國泰航空商務及貨運董事。<br />\n<br />\n何杲表示，收購香港快運對國泰航空集團來說，是具吸引力及務實之舉，有利航空業務的長遠發展，更可壯大香港作為領先國際航空樞紐的競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n他指出：「國泰和香港快運的業務及商業模式大致是互補的。香港快運掌握了一個獨特市場部份，連同國泰航空集團的龐大網絡，令往來香港的航班接駁力以倍數增長，會為廣大旅客帶來莫大裨益，包括更多選擇和更便捷的旅遊體驗。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cathaypacific.com/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BF%AB%E9%81%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA?fbclid=IwAR1U1qTzk_nuQo_JPbsnbvcz7FxTfkiR6Jqc-umLYkN1cr1LuxJwlp_sb9Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cathaypacific.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1U1qTzk_nuQo_JPbsnbvcz7FxTfkiR6Jqc-umLYkN1cr1LuxJwlp_sb9Y&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83Jx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=a1f05cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cathaypacific.com/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BF%AB%E9%81%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA?fbclid=IwAR1U1qTzk_nuQo_JPbsnbvcz7FxTfkiR6Jqc-umLYkN1cr1LuxJwlp_sb9Y</a>"},{"pid":"1d720826934c2625885973540979882af8c5017a","tid":1333332,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"平機票呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5421c963eb726508a5d0c9dc9348143a6344b518","tid":1333332,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"Hx唔知會唔會執左佢呢 聽聞蝕得好甘下"},{"pid":"cf803bf4f66903b997c3afc751f9585db3de0215","tid":1333332,"uid":201178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5421c963eb726508a5d0c9dc9348143a6344b518","tid":1333332,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"Hx唔知會唔會執左佢呢 聽聞蝕得好甘下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d99fbd6b7ce46b8a937a1c82e2148d829477ea","tid":1333332,"uid":57407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:07:32.000Z","msg":"因運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabf752f48f86007f239743786da28f6d5d1c833","tid":1333332,"uid":121085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cf803bf4f66903b997c3afc751f9585db3de0215","tid":1333332,"uid":201178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5421c963eb726508a5d0c9dc9348143a6344b518","tid":1333332,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"Hx唔知會唔會執左佢呢 聽聞蝕得好甘下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"中資唔識做生意<br />\n叫阿爺放水就識"},{"pid":"b5c75ba4a4f681562ad799e